data.description: Under contract-accepting backup offers. NO HOA , NO CDD . Seller Very Motivated !!!!! Bring you offers .BIG PRICE IMPROVEMENT !  This charming Above Ground Pool house located at The Heart of Tampa Bay is a true gem that is now available for sale. Nestled in a peaceful and sought-after neighborhood, this property offers a wonderful opportunity for those in search of a cozy 3 Bedroom 2 bathroom and comfortable home.Perfect for First Time Home Buyers.  Built with meticulous attention to detail, creating a welcoming and inviting curb appeal. A well-maintained .As you step inside, you are greeted by a warm and inviting atmosphere. The spacious living area is bathed in an abundance of natural light, creating a bright and cheerful ambiance. The open floor plan effortlessly connects the living room, dining area, and kitchen, making it perfect for entertaining friends and family. The kitchen is a true centerpiece, equipped with modern appliances, ample counter space, and plenty of storage options. Here, aspiring chefs can prepare culinary delights with ease, while still being a part of the conversations and activities happening in the adjacent living and dining areas.  This house offers three comfortable bedrooms, each providing a peaceful retreat at the end of the day. The master bedroom features its own ensuite bathroom,With plenty of closet space throughout the house, there will be no shortage of storage options.  For those who value outdoor living, this property offers a spacious backyard, with a Above Ground Pool ,perfect for hosting barbecues or enjoying a quiet morning coffee.Conveniently located in the heart of Tampa, this property is just moments away from schools, parks, Tampa International Airport, Bush Garden Attractions, Adventure Island Water Park, shopping centers, and other essential amenities. With easy access to major roads and highways, commuting to downtown Tampa or other parts of the city is a breeze.  Don't miss the opportunity to make this house your own. Call now to schedule a private viewing and experience all that 1903 Heather Ave. has to offer.
